Name: Neon Void Runner
About the game: Neon Void Runner NeonVoid Runner is a infinite runner in which the player will test their reaction time in a fast virtual reality race placed in a futurist synthwave neon world . A lot of obstacles, various levels that open as you progress and of course crazy speeds await you! Player controls one of the stylized runners that can jump, slide and run. And they run faster each time player reach a checkpoint in a level. Sometimes you may encounter a blocking wall, but our characters have the power to shoot an energy ball that destroys then. How to Play: Up - Jump Down - Slide Right - Shoot energy ball. FEATURES : - Synthwave neon stylized graphics - Amazing soundtrack. - Supersonic speeds. - Hard reaction time challenges - Achievements - Various levels
